snippet.title: Star Revenge 1 - Course 1: Grassy Valley
snippet.description:
Star Revenge: Star Takeover is an SM64 hack by BroDute. In this video I complete course 1 of the hack without savestates. Stars are at these times:

0:41 - Star 1 - Big Bob-Omb's Brother
2:17 - Star 2 - From Column to Column
2:54 - Star 3 - Extreme Walljumping
3:34 - Star 4 - Dangerous Narrow Pathway
4:31 - Star 5 - Get the 8 Orange Coins
6:22 - Star 6 - Fly Through the Rings + 100 Coins
